author: steveking
msg: Handle Git patches that contain an index line after the file mode line.
(svn_diff_parse_next_patch): treat the index patch line as a valid
header line that's still part of the current header.

author: steveking
msg: Fix an issue with added files in git patches.
(svn_diff_parse_next_patch): skip the line length check and allow the
patch line to be of equal length as the expected input as well.
